        },
        {
            "title": "日本財務大臣片山皋月稱將在必要時就匯率問題與美國協調應對",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"日本財務大臣片山皋月稱將在必要時就匯率問題與美國協調應對\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Ke8wb1Bc31bhsIhSgbrCUA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-11/7babcd60-c42b-11f0-befe-b99a9ad2cfa7\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">日本財務大臣片山皋月稱將在必要時就匯率問題與美國協調應對</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%B2%A1%E5%8B%99%E5%A4%A7%E8%87%A3%E7%89%87%E5%B1%B1%E7%9A%8B%E6%9C%88%E7%A8%B1%E5%B0%87%E5%9C%A8%E5%BF%85%E8%A6%81%E6%99%82%E5%B0%B1%E5%8C%AF%E7%8E%87%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E8%88%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%8D%94%E8%AA%BF%E6%87%89%E5%B0%8D-012636592.html",
